      <h3>The Craft</h3>
      <p>Every frame is designed in-house and printed layer by layer using premium PLA filament. The result is a frame with clean lines, precise angles, and a modern matte finish that complements any artwork.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3>The Technology</h3>
      <p>We use FDM (Fused Deposition Modeling) 3D printing — the same technology used in aerospace and industrial design. Each frame goes through quality control to ensure dimensional accuracy within 0.2mm.</p>
    </div>
